92 sinh ra \\u00f4ng Huy Thi\\u1ec7p (\\u011011) sinh ra c\\u00e1c anh<\\/p><p>Ti\\u1ec7p, Ti\\u1ebfp (\\u011012)<\\/p><p>2. C\\u1ee5 Huy M\\u00e3 \\u2192 sinh ra c\\u1ee5 Huy B\\u00ecnh, Huy Nhi\\u1ec5m, Huy Ki\\u1ec7m, Huy B\\u00e1i (\\u01107).<\\/p><p>2.1. C\\u1ee5 Huy B\\u00ecnh \\u2192 sinh ra c\\u1ee5 Huy Tr\\u1ea1ch (\\u01108) \\u2014 sinh ra c\\u00e1c c\\u1ee5 Huy An, Huy L\\u1ef1c (ho\\u1eb7c Oa), Th\\u1ecb... (\\u01109).<\\/p><p>C\\u1ee5 Huy An \\u2014 sinh ra c\\u00e1c c\\u1ee5 Th\\u1ecb Ch\\u00e1u, Huy Nghi (\\u011010).<\\/p><p>2.2. C\\u1ee5 Huy Nhi\\u1ec5m \\u2192 sinh ra c\\u00e1c c\\u1ee5 Huy Khi\\u00eam, Huy Phong (Bang),<\\/p><p>Huy Gia (\\u01108).<\\/p><p>2.2.1. C\\u1ee5 Huy Khi\\u00eam \\u2192 sinh ra c\\u00e1c c\\u1ee5 Huy T\\u1ed1n, Huy Qu\\u1ef9 (\\u01109).<\\/p><p>2.2.2. C\\u1ee5 Huy Phong \\u2014 sinh ra c\\u00e1c c\\u1ee5 Huy B\\u00edch, Huy Ki\\u1ec3n (ho\\u1eb7c Gi\\u1ea3n) (\\u01109).<\\/p><p>C\\u1ee5 Huy B\\u00edch sinh ra \\u00f4ng Huy Quy\\u00ean (\\u011010).<\\/p><p>2.2.3. C\\u1ee5 Huy Gia \\u2192 sinh ra c\\u00e1c c\\u1ee5 Huy Hi\\u1ec3u, Huy Nghi\\u1ec5n, Huy Th\\u00e2n, Huy Tu (\\u01109).<\\/p><p>2.2.3.1. C\\u1ee5 Huy Hi\\u1ec3u \\u2014 sinh ra c\\u00e1c c\\u1ee5 Huy M\\u1eadu, Huy \\u0110\\u1ecf (ho\\u1eb7c Ty,ho\\u1eb7c K\\u1ef7) (\\u011010).<\\/p><p>2.2.3.2. C\\u1ee5 Huy Nghi\\u1ec5n 1 \\u2192 sinh ra c\\u1ee5 Huy Tu\\u1ea5t (\\u011010).<\\/p><p>2.2.3.4. C\\u1ee5 Huy Tu \\u2014 sinh ra c\\u1ee5 Huy D\\u0169ng (\\u011010).<\\/p><p>2.3. C\\u1ee5 Huy Ki\\u1ec7m \\u2192 sinh ra c\\u00e1c c\\u1ee5 Huy Li\\u1ec5u, Huy Canh (\\u01108). 2.3.1. C\\u1ee5 Huy Li\\u1ec5u \\u2014 sinh ra c\\u00e1c c\\u1ee5 Huy Oanh, Huy O\\u00e1nh, Huy C\\u01b0\\u1eddng (\\u01109).<\\/p><p>C\\u1ee5 Huy O\\u00e1nh \\u2014 sinh ra Huy Thi\\u1ebft (\\u011010) \\u2014 sinh ra Huy Nh\\u1ef1 (\\u011011).<\\/p><p>2.3.2. C\\u1ee5 Huy Canh \\u2014 sinh ra c\\u00e1c c\\u1ee5 Huy T\\u00e2n, Huy T\\u1ea1o (t\\u1ee9c Li\\u00eau) (\\u01109).<\\/p><p>2.4. C\\u1ee5 Huy B\\u00e1i \\u2014 sinh ra c\\u00e1c c\\u1ee5 Huy Thi\\u1ebfu, Huy Ty (\\u01108).<\\/p><p>2.4.1. C\\u1ee5 Huy Thi\\u1ebfu \\u2192 sinh ra c\\u1ee5 Huy Hi\\u1ebfu, Huy Thung (\\u01109) C\\u1ee5 Huy Hi\\u1ebfu \\u2192 sinh ra c\\u1ee5 Huy Ngh\\u0129a (\\u011010) \\u2014 sinh ra c\\u00e1c \\u00f4ng Sam, Sua, Bu\\u00f2ng...(D11).<\\/p><p>2.4.2. C\\u1ee5 Huy Ty \\u2192 sinh ra c\\u1ee5 Huy Huy\\u1ec1n (\\u01109).<\\/p><p>Chi c\\u1ee5 C\\u1ed1ng Hai hi\\u1ec7n nay do anh Ph\\u1ea1m V\\u0103n Ti\\u1ec7p (con \\u00f4ng Thi\\u1ec7p) l\\u00e0m t\\u1ed9c tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng).<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
